## Schema Conformance Requirements

<!-- CUSTOMIZE: Document your data schema rules -->

### Required Resources

| Resource | Purpose |
|----------|---------|
| `SCHEMA_CATALOG.md` | Source of truth for ALL tables |
| `FIELD_ALIGNMENT_GUIDE.md` | Developer playbook with templates |

### Golden Rules

**MUST DO:**
- Use exact column names from schema catalog
- Include appropriate filters in queries
- Check NULL constraints before inserting

**NEVER DO:**
- Use field aliases
- Query deprecated/legacy tables
- Trust code definitions over the catalog

### Critical Field Names

<!-- CUSTOMIZE: Add your field name conventions -->

| DON'T Use | USE This | Table |
|-----------|----------|-------|
| `doc_id` | `document_uuid` | `documents` |
| `user_id` | `user_uuid` | `users` |

